rComments: Anne is a super nice teacher, she is really understanding and goes above and beyond to help. Her conferences are really helpful. This class was pretty easy, only 3 papers all semester.

Anne is an interesting teacher. Her class is really easy, very little homework, easy grading, and she just wants you to try. She's one of the nicest people ever, very understanding/caring, but to the point that she's almost too nice and easy, especially for upper-division. You will only learn based off how much you AND your classmates care to learn
